          .col-md-6.col-12.order-first.wow.fadeInRight(data-wow-duration="1s")
            .features-scroller__text
              h3 Enable a personal assistant for every customer
              p Turn voice enabled devices and voice assistants on your customer's mobile into their digital personal assistants by connecting your company's service, support and other interaction channels. Your customer's entire brand experience is now as simple as 'Just Asking'.
              b 
                span.features-scroller__text--color 80%
                strong Jump in customer convenience and interactions when brands enable voice based customer support.
        .row.features-scroller__row
          .col-md-6.col-12.wow.fadeInLeft(data-wow-duration="1s")
            .features-scroller__text
              h3 Voice bots that provide 24/7 customer support
              p Your customers may need support at any time of day and keeping agents at full capacity affects long term business revenue. Give your customers voice interfaces that answers their queries in a natural conversational flow, just like a customer support respresentative.
              b 
                span.features-scroller__text--color 30%
                strong Savings in customer support costs with voice bots that work round the clock reducing human resource.
          .col-md-6.col-12.animateme.scrollme(data-when="span" data-from="0" data-to="1" data-easing="linear" data-translatey="-100" style="position: relative;top: 70px")
            .features-scroller__img-voice
