        .row.features-scroller__row
          .col-md-5.col-12.order-md-first.animateme.scrollme(data-when="span" data-from="0" data-to="1" data-easing="linear" data-translatey="-100" style="position: relative;top: 70px")
            .features-scroller__img-voice
              img(src="img/voice/voice-illustration-3.png", alt="")
          .col-md-6.offset-md-1.col-12.order-first.wow.fadeInRight(data-wow-duration="1s")
            .features-scroller__text
              h3 Talk to your customers in the language they prefer
              p Take personalization deeper with a localized flavor to your customer interactions. Leverage localization algorithms and natural language understanding technology to let customers talk to you in their own language.
              b 
                span.features-scroller__text--color 3x
                strong Increase in customer engagement when businesses talk to their customers in local languages.
        .row.features-scroller__row
          .col-md-6.col-12.wow.fadeInLeft(data-wow-duration="1s")
            .features-scroller__text
              h3 Never put your<br> customers on hold ever again
              p Your customers hate waiting! On hold, for answers or for transactions to be completed. It's the No.1 reason why they abandon brands. Adopting voice technology eliminates wait times, untangles them from IVRs and gets them the answers they need in an instant.
              b 
                span.features-scroller__text--color 55%
                strong Of customers dropout of support calls if they are made to wait on hold for more than 3 minutes.
          .col-md-6.col-12.animateme.scrollme(data-when="span" data-from="0" data-to="1" data-easing="linear" data-translatey="-100" style="position: relative;top: 70px")
            .features-scroller__img-voice
              img(src="img/voice/voice-illustration-4.png", alt="")
        .row.features-scroller__row
          .col-md-5.col-12.order-md-first.animateme.scrollme(data-when="span" data-from="0" data-to="1" data-easing="linear" data-translatey="-100" style="position: relative;top: 70px")
            .features-scroller__img-voice
              img(src="img/voice/voice-illustration-5.png", alt="")
          .col-md-6.offset-md-1.col-12.order-first.wow.fadeInRight(data-wow-duration="1s")
            .features-scroller__text
              h3 Give your brand a voice of its own
              p Business growth is all about relationships. Voice tech helps you create a tailored brand tone that humanizes your brand identity. Customers love real relationships and voice tech allows you to add the missing human touch to otherwise cold digital relationships.
              b 
                span 5x
                strong Increase in brand loyalty when customers encounter humanized brand experiences.
